= Errata Tool Docs

This is the RDoc generated documentation for the Errata Tool Rails application.

The HTTP API for creating and modifying advisories is documented at:
* Api::V1::ErratumController

Additional public APIs may be found under the namespace:
* Api::V1

However the primary source of documentation for the above APIs is the Developer
Guide:
* https://errata.devel.redhat.com/developer-guide/

The XML-RPC API information can be found at:
* ErrataService
* SecureService
* PubService
* TpsService

The main index page contains a full list of classes and methods and is located at:
* https://errata.devel.redhat.com/rdoc/

Further information on Errata Tool can be found at:
* https://errata.devel.redhat.com/user-guide/
* https://docs.engineering.redhat.com/display/HTD/Errata+Tool
